title: Northwestern Lehigh's JD Haaf is lehighvalleylive Boys Soccer Player of the Week
text:
The senior forward is the centerpiece of the Tigers offense and led the Colonial League North Division leaders to a 3-0 week over South Division foes. 
Haaf had six goals and an assist as Northwestern topped Moravian Academy, Southern Lehigh and Palisades. 
He scored all three of his teamâ€™s goals in the 3-1 triumph over the Spartans. 
Honorable mention : Sr. FWD Zachary Adams , Salisbury; Sr. FWD Gino Boscia , Pen Argyl; Sr. FWD John Fritz , Emmaus; Jr. MID Kacper Grycel , Emmaus; Sr. MID Keegan Halloran , Phillipsburg; So. FWD Eli Kalfaian , Delaware Valley; Sr. MID/FWD Tyler Madeira , Parkland; Sr. DEF Paxton Ramsey , Bangor; Sr. FWD Steven Riad , Freedom; Sr. DEF Joe Takacs , Phillipsburg; Sr. FWD Michael Visperas , Liberty.
